Location of this README file: /SITE/PROJECT/src

========= Front-End Stylesheets for WEB UI presentation layer ===========

This directory contains the SASS stylesheets developed in teh 1st phase of the EZID
UI Redesign. A certain portion of these stylesheets are still in play, notably:

 _variables.scss
 _bootstrap.scss
 Files in the 'bootstrap' directory

Much of the other files in this directory are slowly being replaced by code 
developed under the 'SITE/PROJECT/dev' directory, initiated by Joel Hagedorn, 
now, as of this writing, being handed off to Andy Mardesich.

In this interim phase, we include styles from both development efforts,

= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = 
main.css (legacy) stylesheet compilation process:

SASS is a scripting language that is interpreted into CSS stylesheets (http://sass-lang.com/)
EZID (development build only) includes libsass python extension module for processing SassScript.

To build CSS from SASS (.scss) files:
sassc ~/apache/ezid/SITE/PROJECT/src/styles/main.scss ~/apache/ezid/SITE/PROJECT/static/stylesheets/main.css


= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = 
main2.css stylesheet/javascript compilation process:

https://github.com/JoelCDL/gulp_template
